e content that will evoke deeply relatable emotions and passion in others.', 5043, 0), (136874, 'Life is easy for some, hard for others. Some succeed with minimal effort, others have to put in a lot of efforts and some have it served in a dish. Whichever your case is, make the best of it. Enjoy the journey.You can''t control the side of life you fall into but you can rise beyond any limitation it places on you. Those who have it easy are made of plastic, you are made of steel. Do what you must today.', 10250, 0), (136875, 'Relaxation is good, holidays are necessary, but there is nothing as rewarding and healthy as doing what you love and loving what you do. Our honest toil should inspire and satisfy us.', 1660, 0), (136876, 'We must pursue knowledge and wisdom above all other things.', 2878, 0), (136877, 'I could not tell anymore how much of the screaming came from my own mouth. I was borne up on the swell of it, I was the sound. We were all howling together, the poor and the quality, the boxing girl and the beast inside my breast. If she was a madwoman, then we were all of us with her, and I had never felt such savage elation, nor known that it existed.', 25996, 0), (136878, 'In today''s globalized world nothing is sure. Routines are falling', 25997, 0), (136879, 'We are capable of performing the task.', 2878, 0), (136880, 'Every path that my foot has treaded was divinely ordered.', 2878, 0), (136881, 'I do not mind sleepless night to be involved in reading.', 2878, 0), (136882, 'Encouragement fuels great strength and great achievement.', 2878, 0), (136883, 'You are born with a crown.Create your own kingdom!', 16935, 0), (136884, 'You must pursue your dreams with all your might.', 2878, 0), (136885, 'I am giving my all in all to the sacred moments.', 2878, 0), (136886, 'Written words are divine footprints on earth.', 2878, 0), (136887, 'Whether you sweep the toilet of a school or you make cloths. Whether you take pictures of dancers or you are a full-time house wif